00:00:20.510 --> 00:00:23.150
And today, he'll share his
creative process and inspire

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:25.760
you in this journey
of discovery.

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:28.560
And one of my favorite quotes
of JP's is, "How the artist

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:31.390
